snippet.title: Eye of the Temple - Official Launch Trailer (Meta Quest)
snippet.description:
Oculus Store ▶ https://www.oculus.com/experiences/quest/5361030930653377/
Discord ▶ https://discord.gg/yGN7bDQ
Twitter ▶ https://twitter.com/eyeofthetemple
TikTok ▶ https://www.tiktok.com/@eyeofthetemple

Embark on a VR adventure to explore a vast and treacherous temple and uncover the ancient legend of the Eye. Keep your balance as you step between moving blocks, dodging hazardous traps and solving environmental puzzles with just your torch and whip in hand.

A game by Rune Skovbo Johansen. Music by Claudi Martinez. Voice of The Guardian by Gina Scarpa. Co-developed for Quest by Salmi Games. Mixed reality footage by Anaburn.
